Shameless suckless 2f30.org noice fork.

1. Selected entry highlighting.
2. 4 columns rendering with Space, L/H switching.
3. Cyclic scrolling.
4. Renamed binary noice -> yesfire.

alias y=yesfire >> .zshrc

Fuck mc, vifm, ranger, nerdtree and other stuff.

Now it's the best and only four column file manager in
the world. Seriously.

See it working on Windows 10: https://i.imgur.com/1uQB508.png
Also it runs even on the Android smartphones via Termux.

